DarkMouse::

"Yes, as you command." She turned and walked away. She opened her 
link,"Famine, where are you?  I'm on my way to help tote supplies."
She had a frustrated tone in her voice.  She couldn't understand why 
things were going the way they were.  And since she didn't 
understand, it made her alittle angry at herself.  She was usually 
good at figuring things out, but this time, things were going against 
predacon and maximal nature.  This bothered her.  She muttered, "what 
is this world coming to?"
